
Non-empty case without break is suspicios
=========================================

::

    switch(foo) {
        case 0:        // <- this is probably ok
        case 1:
            bar();
            break;

        case 2:
            baz();     // <- this is suspicious
        case 3:
            xyzzy();
            break;
        
        case 4:
            baz();
            // nobreak    <- this is clearly intentional
        case 5:
            xyzzy();
            break;
    }

Scope reduce
============

::

    {
        int i;
        {
            // i should be declared here
            i = 0;
        }
    }

